{- Note [%shift: aexp2 -> ipvar]
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Context:
    aexp2 -> ipvar .
    dbind -> ipvar . '=' exp

Example:
    let ?x = ...

Ambiguity:
    If we reduced, ?x would be parsed as the LHS of a normal binding,
    eventually producing an error.

    We shift, so it is parsed as the LHS of an implicit binding.
